                <h2>Welcome</h2>
                <p>Welcome to my academic homepage. I am an Assistant Professor of Classical Studies at [Your University], specializing in Roman literature, ancient historiography, and digital humanities approaches to classical texts.</p>
                
                <p>My research focuses on the intersection of literature and politics in the Late Republic, with particular attention to how historical narratives shaped and reflected contemporary political discourse. I am currently working on a monograph examining the rhetorical strategies employed by ancient historians in their accounts of civil conflict.</p>
                
